WEBVTT

02:17:37.358 --> 02:17:39.691
I told him clearly,
no communication over the phone.

02:17:39.733 --> 02:17:40.441
What about Avira?

02:17:40.483 --> 02:17:41.941
He might be on the way
to Rameswaram.

02:17:41.983 --> 02:17:42.983
Are you sure?

02:17:43.108 --> 02:17:44.108
That was my plan.
